title: MAC Is Adding 3 New Shades to the Extra Dimension Skinfinish Highlighter Collection
text:
Another day, another new MAC product to add to my list of makeup to buy. Beauty Instagram account TrendMood1 teased a photo of a few new highlighter shades by the brand, and you won't be able to stop staring at them.

Advertisement - Continue Reading Below The new additions consist of a bronze shade called "Hard to Get, " a peachy champagne shade called "Fairly Precious," and pretty pink shade called "Into the Pink," which could double as a gorgeous blush shade. *Sold.*
After trying and loving the four shades of the Extra Dimension Skinfinish highlighter that launched last November, I have no doubt that these will be pretty baller too.
If you're stressing because you have to pay rent soon, don't worry because you have a until fall to save up for this launch. The new shades are still being tested backstage, so MAC doesn't have too many details to share just yet. Check back for updates though.
